headline: EPR Properties (EPR) Q3 FFO Beat Estimates
summary: EPR Properties (EPR) delivered FFO and revenue surprises of +5.30% and -1.53%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
